description: Acrinova AB engages in the ownership, construction, and management of real estate. The company is headquartered in Malmo, Skane. The company went IPO on 2015-03-02. The firm owns, operates and develops logistic properties. Its primary activities comprise property ownership in Southern Sweden, management of own and others’ properties, as well as development and construction of new, mostly residential, buildings. The Company’s customers are primarily logistics and secondary e-commerce stores and portals. The firm is operative through subsidiaries, which include Norama Asset Management AB, Norama Projektutveckling AB, Acrinova Stamhogen AB, Acrinova Bokbindaren AB and Lundgrens Montage I Hjarup AB. The main shareholder in the Company is Malmohus Invest AB.
